      <p>1.11&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"DropsTec&nbsp;Hub" means the technology platform operated and maintained by&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;which connects customers requiring the Delivery of a Drop to Drivers who make their services available to undertake the Delivery and which comprises&nbsp;the&nbsp;&nbsp;App&nbsp;and&nbsp;DropsTec's&nbsp;proprietary backend platform;</p>

      <p>1.12&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"No-Go Area" means an area in which a Delivery Address is situated which is not safe for a Driver to make deliveries, as reasonably determined by&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;from time to&nbsp;time;</p>

      <p>1.13&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"Payload Specifications" means the specifications within which each Drop must fall&nbsp;in order to&nbsp;qualify for delivery by the Drivers, being:</p>

