      <p>1.14.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;where a Driver arrives at the Pick-up Point within 15 minutes of the designated time and the Drop is not available at the Pick-up Point within 10 minutes of arrival by the Driver, despite reasonable attempts by the Driver to contact the sender of the Drop.&nbsp;&nbsp;This includes where You have provided an incorrect Pick-up&nbsp;Point;</p>

      <p>1.14.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;where a Driver arrives at a Delivery Address within 15 minutes of the designated time and the recipient is not available at the Delivery Address within 10 minutes of arrival by the Driver despite reasonable attempts by the Driver to contact the designated recipient. This includes where You have provided an incorrect Delivery&nbsp;Address;</p>

      <p>1.15&nbsp;shall have the meaning ascribed thereto in POPI from time to&nbsp;time;</p>

      <p>1.16"" means the Protection of Personal Information Act 4 of&nbsp;2013;</p>

      <p>1.17&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"Prohibited Items" means those items which may not be included in any Drop by You under any circumstances, including, without limitation:</p>

