      <p>2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b></b>Applicability of this DDA</b></p>

      <p>2.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The terms of this DDA shall apply to every Drops Drive undertaken by a Driver&nbsp;in response to a Request submitted by You.</p>

      <p>2.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You understand and acknowledge that&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;may change these terms from time to time by publishing revised terms on the App.&nbsp;&nbsp;By submitting a Request,&nbsp;You&nbsp;agree to the terms and conditions which are in operation on the date such Request is submitted.</p>

