      <p>3.2.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;to notify&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;of any change in the details submitted when You Register.&nbsp;&nbsp;You assume all liability for any failure by a Driver to deliver which arises out of the fact that You have not updated any&nbsp;information&nbsp;or You have supplied incorrect information at Registration, or any time thereafter;</p>

