      <p>3.2.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;to keep all log-in and username details secret and confidential and You accept that any transactions&nbsp;entered into, including all Requests submitted and payments made using such log-in details, shall be binding on You and conclusively be deemed to have been undertaken by You.</p>

      <p>4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Services</b></p>

      <p>4.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The nature of the services shall be as follows:</p>

      <p>4.1.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;will, through the&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;Hub, procure the Delivery of Drops by a Driver and shall arrange for the collection of each Drop from the designated Pickup Point and the Delivery of such Drop to the Delivery Address by a Driver.</p>

      <p>4.1.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In order to request a Drop Drive,&nbsp;You&nbsp;shall submit a Request via the App.&nbsp;</p>

      <p>4.1.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You will be given a quote at the time Your Request is submitted, based on the distance between the Pickup Point and the Delivery Address.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you accept the quote, you will be billed on the basis set out in paragraph&nbsp;6.</p>

      <p>4.1.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You may cancel any Delivery via the App up until the time the relevant Driver is dispatched, at which stage the full Delivery Fee is payable.</p>

      <p>4.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Notwithstanding the above, a Driver may refuse to deliver any Drop if:</p>

      <p>4.2.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the Drop exceeds the Payload&nbsp;Specifications;</p>

      <p>4.2.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the Drop contains Prohibited&nbsp;Items;</p>

      <p>4.2.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the relevant Delivery Address is in a No-Go&nbsp;Area;&nbsp;</p>

      <p>provided that in the circumstances contemplated in clauses&nbsp;4.2.1&nbsp;or&nbsp;4.2.2,&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;shall nonetheless be entitled to charge a Cancellation Fee.</p>

      <p>5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Your Obligations.&nbsp;&nbsp;In order to&nbsp;utilise a Drops Drive, You must:</b></p>

      <p>5.1ensure that each Drop complies with the Payload Specifications and does not contain any Prohibited Items.&nbsp;&nbsp;You must reveal the contents of any Drop on the request of the Driver, who may refuse to convey the Drop if You refuse to reveal the content when&nbsp;requested;</p>

      <p>5.2pack Your Drop to adequately to protect the contents from damage.&nbsp;&nbsp;Neither&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;nor the Driver shall be liable for any damage to the contents of a Drop if You have failed to pack them appropriately and You hereby indemnify&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;and the Driver against any loss, harm or damage which may arise as a result&nbsp;thereof;</p>

      <p>5.3affix Your full contact and address details to the Drop, as well as the full contact and address details of the intended&nbsp;recipient;&nbsp;</p>

      <p>5.4inform&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;of any internal security or other procedures which are required with regard to the collection and/or delivery of Drops by&nbsp;Drivers;</p>

      <p>5.5reasonably co-operate with&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;and any Driver dispatched to Deliver Your&nbsp;Drop;</p>

      <p>5.6make the Drop available to the Driver timeously at the Pick-up Point at the designated pickup time so as not to cause him to wait unnecessarily.&nbsp;&nbsp;You acknowledge that the Driver shall not be required to wait for more than 10 minutes to collect a Drop.&nbsp;&nbsp;Thereafter the Driver shall be entitled to leave the Pick-up Point and You shall be charged for the Delivery; and</p>

      <p>5.7ensure that the intended recipient of a Drop is aware of its impending delivery and is available to take delivery of the Drop.&nbsp;&nbsp;You acknowledge that the Driver shall not be required to wait for more than 10 minutes to deliver a Drop.&nbsp;&nbsp;Thereafter the Driver shall be entitled to leave the Delivery Address and You shall be charged for the Delivery.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you require the Drop to be redelivered or returned, an additional Delivery Fee will be payable.</p>

      <p>6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Consideration.&nbsp;&nbsp;Upon the occurrence of a Payment Trigger, you will be billed for the Drop Drive (or Cancellation Fee if appropriate) You have requested.&nbsp;&nbsp;Please note that payments are processed by a third party and your payment will be subject to any terms and conditions imposed by the payment processor.</p>

      <p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Relief Event.</b></p>

      <p>7.1If the ability of the Driver to Deliver a Drop is prevented or delayed by any Relief Event, neither&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;nor the Driver shall be liable for any costs, charges or losses sustained or incurred by You that arise directly or indirectly from such Relief Event and&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;shall be entitled to charge the relevant Delivery Fee despite any such prevention or delay and&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;shall be entitled to recover from You any additional costs, charges or losses which&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;or a Driver sustains that arise from such Relief Event.</p>

      <p>7.2Where a Driver encounters or suffers a Relief Event,&nbsp;You&nbsp;will be notified thereof within a reasonable period of time, including any additional amount which may become payable.</p>

      <p>8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Risk and ownership of Drop.&nbsp;Risk in and ownership of a Drop shall at no time vest in&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;or the Driver and under no circumstances whatsoever shall&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;or any Driver be liable for any loss,&nbsp;harm&nbsp;or damage to a Drop.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is incumbent on you to ensure that any valuable consignment is appropriately insured against loss or damage.</p>

