      <p>13.1DropsTec will collect, use, access, maintain, and disclose or share Your Personal Information, including that of third parties supplied by You ("") only to the extent strictly necessary to perform its obligations under this DDA, or as otherwise required by law.&nbsp;&nbsp;DropsTec&nbsp;shall not otherwise use,&nbsp;copy&nbsp;or modify Your Personal Information, merge it with other data, commercially exploit it, disclose it, or do any other thing that may in any manner adversely affect the integrity, security or confidentiality of Your Personal Information, other than as expressly specified herein.</p>

