      <p>19.7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Each party shall be responsible for its own legal and other costs relating to the negotiation of this Agreement.</p>

      <p>19.8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Headings and sub-headings are inserted for information purposes only and shall not be used in the interpretation of this Agreement.</p>

